{"tid":203750,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日三餐 16/04/2017","createTime":"2017-04-16T13:51:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T01:59:05.000Z","uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e5e78a1de797f36512bd50e8a46ad0e4c592c30a","tid":203750,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T13:51:59.000Z","msg":"胃潰瘍好得7788 終於有番啲胃口食野<br />\n本身已經瘦底 依家病完得番100磅鬆啲<br />\n想試下係度記錄低自己每日食過既野<br />\n順便提醒自己每日要食多啲<br />\n<br />\n#早餐<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/214101_6e8513ec7546476e94cb9a9fcba73648.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F214101_6e8513ec7546476e94cb9a9fcba73648.jpg&h=1624f5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清腸胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#午餐 #又係自助餐加火鍋<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/214134_6d0f74b874bae08575aa00c8fc4a3d4d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F214134_6d0f74b874bae08575aa00c8fc4a3d4d.jpg&h=ef2ad2ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係食啲肉食啲菜食碗飯咁<br />\n<br />\n#下午茶<br />\n薑汁撞奶<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n6n59py.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn6n59py.jpg&h=fa60e457&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好滑 夠薑味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n#晚餐 <br />\n5點幾散團之後就過關番香港 <br />\n親戚釣左十幾條唔知咩班 湯左條黎食<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/16/214231_e0fdb2c8745030ca20012a2d630c9dd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F16%2F214231_e0fdb2c8745030ca20012a2d630c9dd4.jpg&h=e188ad20&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4fa62824b4fbc5e589b32b44a3f0ca8cb8e7d6c6","tid":203750,"uid":72872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:56:25.000Z","msg":"正呀薑汁撞奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d667757831cabae178a0a3e484b3ab793243e6ec","tid":203750,"uid":79870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"是日四餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35eb3b295de1a56cf0fb806f82f5db38da651c4","tid":203750,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:16:22.000Z","msg":"去左邊，點解日日打邊邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2adc4c3df323b52ba95c761e928bea0b5f2829bf","tid":203750,"uid":10330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:17:57.000Z","msg":"你就好 咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede126ea1b0122a79ffefd720e4a1e348dfc97d7","tid":203750,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T15:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你就好 咁瘦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9bd890ec66ecfc2d13bac43a2e52e33a338b63","tid":203750,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正呀薑汁撞奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似剝殼雞蛋咁滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69383ab59fc591429bc4c56eb0e4103fbe640a8a","tid":203750,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T01:55:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是日四餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bead5e05f1ed25ef2cfeeb05f1c09226871673c","tid":203750,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit